title: [Kenstrom's Bureau]
description: Standing to both sides of ornate double doors are two elven barmaids, their curly red hair hanging over their emerald eyes, eternal smiles shaped upon their ivory faces.  A large aquarium runs the length of an entire wall, its waters clean but only skeletal fish littering the bottom of the tank.  A circular navy blue rug leads up to a pair of plush leather chairs which face a wide ebony desk.  Behind the desk sits a closet door covered with alloy chains and a sign reading, "No Skeletons In Here."
